Package org.moeaframework.util.grammar

package org.moeaframework.util.grammar
Utilities for representing, parsing and building grammars for use in Grammatical Evolution (GE).

References:

  1. Ryan, C., Collins, J.J., and O'Neill, M. "Grammatical Evolution: Evolving Programs for an Arbitrary Language." Lecture Notes in Computer Science, Proceedings of the First European Workshop on Genetic Programming, pp. 82-95, 1998.
